    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> meatballs </strong>to a separate<strong> baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) and put the tray[s] in the oven for 15 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
