    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the onion softens, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Once the onion has softened, add your <strong>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano </strong>and your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> with 100ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [150ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until thickened</p>",
